com.epoch.chem

Class ElectronMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • chemaxon.sss.search.MolComparator
      • com.epoch.chem.ElectronMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChemConstants, FormatConstants, LewisConstants

    public final class ElectronMatcher
extends MolComparator
implements LewisConstants
    Alters normal JChem matching behavior so that corresponding atoms in the query and target must have the same number of unshared electrons.
